  "page": "Battle at Kayce",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle at Kayce</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\nAftermath of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/132_AC\" title=\"132 AC\">132&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Kayce\" title=\"Kayce\">Kayce</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nWestermen victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Lannister.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/45px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/60px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Greyjoy.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Greyjoy.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/30px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/45px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Greyjoy.svg/60px-House_Greyjoy.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">House Greyjoy</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Lannister\" title=\"Johanna Lannister\">Johanna Lannister</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a>'s uncle†</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>A <b>battle at Kayce</b> occurred during <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a>'s war against the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Battle\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Battle</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_at_Kayce&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"Lord of the Iron Islands\">Lord of the Iron Islands</a>, attacked the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, raiding <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and invading <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Dalton nearly captured <a href=\"/index.php/Kayce\" title=\"Kayce\">Kayce</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and the Red Kraken took the widow of the <a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Kayce\" title=\"Knight of Kayce\">Knight of Kayce</a> as a <a href=\"/index.php/Salt_wife\" title=\"Salt wife\">salt wife</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Lannister\" title=\"Johanna Lannister\">Johanna Lannister</a>, one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Widows\" title=\"Three Widows\">Three Widows</a>, led the <a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">westermen</a>'s resistance to the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> after the death of her husband, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a>, in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Red_Fork\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle of the Red Fork\">Battle of the Red Fork</a>. According to Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a>, Johanna agreed to make peace with the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Hour_of_the_Wolf\" title=\"Hour of the Wolf\">Hour of the Wolf</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/131_AC\" title=\"131 AC\">131&#160;AC</a> out of concern for the defense of Kayce. In return, Johanna asked for the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> to command Dalton to relinquish captured women and return to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Dalton ignored the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency of Aegon III</a>, however, and attacked Johanna's shipyards when she attempted to build a new <a href=\"/index.php/Lannister_fleet\" title=\"Lannister fleet\">Lannister fleet</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Battle\">Battle</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_at_Kayce&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Battle\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Since Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tyland_Lannister\" title=\"Tyland Lannister\">Tyland Lannister</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> and the late Lord Jason's twin, had been unable to aid the westermen against the ironborn, Lady Johanna donned mail and marched with a host from <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a> to protect Kayce. Singers claim that Johanna killed a dozen ironborn beneath the town's walls, though Gyldayn writes that Johanna instead carried a banner and inspired her men to victory. The ironborn raiders were routed in the battle, with Dalton's favorite uncle among the slain, and Kayce was saved.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_at_Kayce&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Victorious at Kayce, Lady Johanna next planned to recover Fair Isle from the ironborn. Her plan was betrayed to the enemy, however, and the ragtag fleet she sent was defeated in an <a href=\"/index.php/Ambush_at_Fair_Isle\" title=\"Ambush at Fair Isle\">ambush at Fair Isle</a>. As vengeance for his slain uncle, Dalton sent the heads of Johanna's three commanders to Casterly Rock.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_at_Kayce&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - The Red Dragon and the Gold.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Comment by Ran at <i>A Forum of Ice and Fire</i>, <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/34958-the-asoiaf-wiki-thread/&amp;do=findComment&amp;comment=8946110\">The ASOIAF wiki thread</a>, June 02, 2023</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Voyage of Alyn Oakenfist.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aftermath - The Hour of the Wolf.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">6.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\">6.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Hooded Hand.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - War and Peace and Cattle Shows.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404204300\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.075 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.239 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 904/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9705/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10305/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2199/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4729/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.31 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  222.976      1 -total\n 88.62%  197.602      1 Template:Battlebox\n 88.17%  196.599      1 Template:Infobox\n  6.10%   13.597      7 Template:Ref\n  5.51%   12.279      3 Template:Date\n  3.82%    8.520      7 Template:Ref/core\n  1.46%    3.247      1 Template:References\n  1.26%    2.802      1 Templat